4 23:16 UTC = April 15 06:16 UTC+7):\\n\\n\\nQLHV backend has a merge request pending Lead review, while AHV Works still needs P0 fixes and the Stitch MCP wrapper test plus stitch-connect skill update remain on the backlog. The pipeline is running clean with no active subagents, and both the DTLX backend and frontend are stable, though there's no current blocker aside from the QLHV BE MR awaiting review.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**DAILY BRIEFING — Orbis 🌐**\\n📅 Tuesday, April 15, 2026 — 06:16 AM (UTC+7)\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n**STATUS: ✅ HEALTHY**\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n---\\n\\n**① YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED (Apr 14)**\\n\\n| # | Task | Status |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| 1 | DTLX BE Fix — `docs` vs `data` field mismatch | ✅ Fixed across all modules |\\n| 2 | DTLX API Verification — 18/18 endpoints tested | ✅ All passing |\\n| 3 | Pipeline Recovery — gateway timeout & Telegram delivery | ✅ HEALTHY restored |\\n| 4 | Session Cleanup — prior abort instances cleared | ✅ Clean state |\\n| 5 | Students page filter bug | ✅ Fixed |\\n| 6 | Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) | ✅ Running stable |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**② TODAY'S PRIORITIES (Apr 15)**\\n\\n| Priority | Task | Owner |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| 🔴 P0 | QLHV BE MR !6 — Lead review + merge | Lead |\\n| 🟡 P1 | AHV Works — 13 P0 issues pending fix | Agent queue |\\n| 🟡 P1 | Stitch MCP wrapper test | Agent queue |\\n| 🟡 P1 | Update stitch-connect skill | Agent queue |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**③ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n\\n| Item | Status |\\n|---|---|\\n| Telegram delivery (17:40 UTC Apr 14) | ✅ Stable — no current issues |\\n| QLHV BE MR !6 awaiting review | ⏳ Pending Lead action |\\n| No active subagents | ✅ Zero overhead |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**System Summary:**\\n- DTLX BE: Running port 5555 ✅\\n- DTLX FE: Running port 3000 ✅\\n- Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅\\n- Active agents: 0\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n_Orbis 🌐 — 06:16 AM UTC+7_\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api